---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="CrazyQuizzes privacy policy — how we handle your data, cookies, and advertising.">
  <div class="page-badge">★ LEGAL STUFF</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">PRIVACY<br><span style="color:#3bffd2;">POLICY</span></h1>
  <div class="page-body">
    <p><em>Last updated: June 2026</em></p>
    <p>CrazyQuizzes ("we", "us", "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and what rights you have.</p>

    <h2>WHAT WE COLLECT</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Quiz activity:</strong> We do not store your quiz answers or results on our servers. All quiz logic runs in your browser.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> We may collect anonymous analytics data (page views, session length, general location by country) to understand how the site is used. This data is not linked to you personally.</li>
      <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use cookies for site functionality, analytics, and advertising. See the Cookies section below for details.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>COOKIES</h2>
    <p>We use the following types of cookies:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Functional cookies:</strong> Required for the site to work (e.g., storing your cookie consent preference).</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> Help us understand how visitors use the site (e.g., which quizzes are most popular). Data is anonymous and not linked to you personally.</li>
      <li><strong>Advertising cookies:</strong> Used by Google AdSense to serve relevant ads. These cookies may track your browsing activity across sites to show you personalized advertising.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can control or disable cookies through your browser settings. Note that disabling advertising cookies will not remove ads — it will show non-personalized ads instead.</p>

    <h2>ADVERTISING</h2>
    <p>We use <strong>Google AdSense</strong> to display advertisements on this site. Google and its advertising partners use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to this and other websites.</p>
    <p>Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your visits to this site and/or other sites on the internet.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ad Settings</a>.</li>
      <li>You may also opt out via <a href="https://optout.aboutads.info/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">aboutads.info</a> (Digital Advertising Alliance).</li>
      <li>For more information on how Google uses data, see <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener">How Google uses data when you use our partners' sites or apps</a>.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>HOW WE USE YOUR DATA</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To operate and improve the site</li>
      <li>To understand which quizzes are popular</li>
      <li>To serve relevant advertising through Google AdSense</li>
      <li>To fix bugs and technical issues</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not sell your personal data. We do not build marketing lists.</p>

    <h2>THIRD-PARTY SERVICES</h2>
    <p><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — displays advertising. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
    <p><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — serves typefaces. Google may collect data as described in their <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
    <p><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — hosts and delivers the site. Cloudflare may process your IP address as part of their network infrastructure. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

    <h2>YOUR RIGHTS</h2>
    <p>Depending on where you live, you may have rights regarding your personal data, including the right to access, correct, or delete it, and the right to object to certain processing. If you are in the EU/EEA, these rights are protected under the GDPR.</p>
    <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@crazyquizzes.com">hello@crazyquizzes.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>CHILDREN</h2>
    <p>CrazyQuizzes is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us and we will delete it.</p>

    <h2>CHANGES TO THIS POLICY</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of the site after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

    <h2>CONTACT</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy? <a href="/contact">Contact us.</a></p>
  </div>
</Layout>
